 "remarks": "Downtown Stamford Living at Its Best! This fantastic 2-bed, 2-bath home at the Mill River House offers the perfect blend of style, convenience, and tranquility. * The Home: Tucked away on the quiet side of the building with soaring high ceilings, in-unit laundry, and generous walk-in closets in both bedrooms. * Parking: Includes 2 secure parking spaces under the building (1 reserved, 1 floating)-perfectly convenient for any weather. * The Location: Directly across from Mill River Park. Walkable to UConn Stamford, vibrant restaurants, shopping, and entertainment. Minutes to I-95 and the Stamford Train Station. * Building Amenities: Access to a total gym, outdoor courtyard, grilling atrium, and a meeting club room. Don&apos;t miss this opportunity-set up a private viewing today!",
